  <thing id="sogTlExtraFaction" name="Extra Faction Package" compset="SoGTalent" description="You gain the Faction sphere package you do not already have. When you requisition a retainer, you can have the faction equip your retainer in a manner equivalent to an NPC of their level by spending an additional 1 authorization when you request them (see NPCs in Pathfinder Roleplaying Game Core Rulebook or NPC stat blocks in the Pathfinder Roleplaying Game NPC Codex or Pathfinder Roleplaying Game: GameMastery Guide for examples). You also gain the new packageâ€™s skill as an additional associated skill for this sphere." uniqueness="useronce">
