  <thing id="sogTlPotionSupply" name="Potion Supply" compset="SoGTalent" description="Your item requisition can be for any alchemical remedy, elixir, potion, or similar single-use consumable item available in your factionâ€™s area. The potions available match the spellcasting services for your faction type. The itemâ€™s caster level must be no higher than your associated skill ranks â€“ 2.\n\nYou can take this talent a second time if you have at least 10 ranks in Appraise. If you do, you can spend 2 authorizations to requisition any single potion or elixir regardless of your factionâ€™s spellcasting services worth up to your temporary resource budget. The caster level must be no higher than your ranks in Appraise if it suits your factionâ€™s spellcasting services, or no higher than your ranks in Appraise â€“ 2 otherwise.">
