  <thing id="sogTlScrollCache" name="Scroll Cache" compset="SoGTalent" description="You can requisition the following items. Scrolls you requisition canâ€™t have multiple spells with different names on them.\n\n{indent 20}* {b}Single Scroll (2 authorizations):{/b} Any scroll available with your faction typeâ€™s spellcasting. The scrollâ€™s caster level can be up to your associated skill ranks â€“ 2 (minimum 1st). The scrollâ€™s price can be up to twice your temporary resource budget.* {b}Scroll Bundle (2 authorizations):{/b} Three identical scrolls available with your faction typeâ€™s spellcasting with caster level up to your associated skill ranks â€“ 5 (minimum 1st). The sum of their price must be within triple your temporary budget.{indent -20}You can take this talent a second time. If you do, you increase the maximum caster level for your factionâ€™s scrolls by 1." uniqueness="useronce">
