  <thing id="sogTlArt" name="Act" compset="SoGTalent" description="You can begin an act as a move action by adopting the approach associated with it. Starting an act provokes attacks of opportunity. An act grants its effects to all enemies or allies within a 20-foot radius + 5 feet per 5 ranks in this packageâ€™s associated Perform skill for as long as the act is active, up to a maximum of 1 minute.\n\nWhile an act is active, allies in the area that can perceive you may spend actions to contribute to the actâ€™s scenes, completing them. Once a scene has been completed, it confers its effects to the act until it ends, and cannot be completed again (unless otherwise specified).\n\nAll acts have a finale, which requires all of the actâ€™s scenes to be completed before you may use it. Once you activate an actâ€™s finale, it ends the act and its associated benefits other than the finaleâ€™s effects at the end of your next turn.\n\n{b}Associated Skill{/b}: Perform (act or comedy)." summary="Gain the act package" uniqueness="useronce">
