  <thing id="sogTlEntwininPran" name="Entwining Prance" compset="SoGTalent" description="All dancers begin to weave closely around nearby opponents. Whenever an enemy enters the threatened area of a dancer, the dancer may spend an attack of opportunity to force the enemy to succeed at a Reflex save or become entangled until they leave all the dancersâ€™ threatened areas (or until the dance ends)." uniqueness="useronce">
