  <thing id="sogTlAdeptHandler" name="Adept Handler" compset="SoGTalent" description="You only need to spend 1 day to train an animal for the riding purpose (learning the tricks come, heel, and stay), or you may spend 1 use of skill leverage to reduce this to 4 hours. This general purpose does not count towards the animalâ€™s usual maximum of tricks or general purposes they may learn. You halve the time required to teach an animal a trick or general purpose.\n\nAdditionally, when using Handle Animal to command an animal to perform a task or trick, you may do so as a standard action to command a number of animals that can perceive you equal to your ranks in Profession (shepherd or stable master)." uniqueness="useronce">
